                            Purpose of the application

The KiekMolWedderIn web application suports the planning and execution of chess tournaments. 
The main features are
- Master data administration for tournaments, rounds, players
- Planning of tournament rounds and games
- Documentation of game results
- Authoring and publication of game reports
- Automatic calculation of player ranking

